  "title": "Indian menu Chef",
  "description": "<ul><li>Prepare a wide range of authentic Indian dishes South & North Indian cuisine menus, incorporating traditional dishes (including both vegetarian and non-vegetarian options )</li><li>Specialize in curry preparation and tandoor cooking techniques</li><li>Specialize in veg and non-vegetarian Biryani</li><li>Create and update menus, incorporating seasonal ingredients and culinary trends</li><li>Control food and labor costs through efficient portioning, inventory management, and waste reduction strategies while maintaining food quality.</li><li>Monitor food quality and presentation to uphold the restaurant's standards and exceed guest expectations.</li><li>Manage and oversee all kitchen operations, including staff supervision and training</li></ul><p></p><p>Requirements:</p><p></p><ul><li>Minimum 10 yrs of Proven experience as a chef specializing in South & North Indian cuisine, with a minimum of  2 years in a similar role.</li><li>Strong leadership and team management skills</li><li>Good communication skills in English; knowledge of Hindi or other Indian languages is a plus</li><li>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment and handle pressure</li><li>Familiarity with kitchen management software and inventory systems</li><li>Knowledge of food safety regulations and hygiene standards</li></ul><p><br /></p>",
